N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 346.8 - Carriers not to supply names of authorized chiropractors

State Regulations

Insurance carriers shall not supply names of authorized
chiropractors to their policyholders. Employers may secure a list of all
authorized chiropractors in the vicinity of their places of business by
applying to the chairman. Notes
